{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":840,"text":"I'd like to start by asking you all\nto go to your happy place, please."},{"time":5440,"text":"Yes, your happy place,"},{"time":6680,"text":"I know you've got one even if it's fake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":8640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9880,"text":"OK, so, comfortable?"},{"time":11200,"text":"Good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12440,"text":"Now I'd like to you to mentally answer\nthe following questions."},{"time":15880,"text":"Is there any strip lighting\nin your happy place?"},{"time":19080,"text":"Any plastic tables?"},{"time":21160,"text":"Polyester flooring?"},{"time":23000,"text":"Mobile phones?"},{"time":24520,"text":"No?"},{"time":25760,"text":"I think we all know that our happy place"},{"time":27689,"text":"is meant to be\nsomewhere natural, outdoors --"},{"time":30520,"text":"on a beach, fireside."},{"time":32159,"text":"We'll be reading or eating or knitting."},{"time":36280,"text":"And we're surrounded\nby natural light and organic elements."},{"time":40680,"text":"Natural things make us happy."},{"time":43320,"text":"And happiness is a great motivator;\nwe strive for happiness."},{"time":47200,"text":"Perhaps that's why\nwe're always redesigning everything,"},{"time":49840,"text":"in the hopes that our solutions\nmight feel more natural."},{"time":54880,"text":"So let's start there --"},{"time":56360,"text":"with the idea that good design\nshould feel natural."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60800,"text":"Your phone is not very natural."},{"time":65099,"text":"And you probably think\nyou're addicted to your phone,"},{"time":67600,"text":"but you're really not."},{"time":69240,"text":"We're not addicted to devices,"},{"time":71320,"text":"we're addicted to the information\nthat flows through them."},{"time":74680,"text":"I wonder how long you would be\nhappy in your happy place"},{"time":77680,"text":"without any information\nfrom the outside world."},{"time":81520,"text":"I'm interested in how we access\nthat information,"},{"time":83840,"text":"how we experience it."},{"time":85880,"text":"We're moving from a time\nof static information,"},{"time":89920,"text":"held in books and libraries and bus stops,"},{"time":92920,"text":"through a period of digital information,"},{"time":95200,"text":"towards a period of fluid information,"},{"time":97480,"text":"where your children will expect to be able\nto access anything, anywhere at any time,"},{"time":103720,"text":"from quantum physics\nto medieval viticulture,"},{"time":107640,"text":"from gender theory to tomorrow's weather,"},{"time":111520,"text":"just like switching on a lightbulb --"},{"time":114680,"text":"Imagine that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116120,"text":"Humans also like simple tools."},{"time":119320,"text":"Your phone is not a very simple tool."},{"time":122480,"text":"A fork is a simple tool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":125400,"text":"And we don't like them made of plastic,"},{"time":128240,"text":"in the same way I don't really like\nmy phone very much --"},{"time":130931,"text":"it's not how I want\nto experience information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135480,"text":"I think there are better solutions\nthan a world mediated by screens."},{"time":139600,"text":"I don't hate screens, but I don't feel --"},{"time":142040,"text":"and I don't think any of us feel that good"},{"time":144080,"text":"about how much time\nwe spend slouched over them."},{"time":148160,"text":"Fortunately,"},{"time":149440,"text":"the big tech companies seem to agree."},{"time":151240,"text":"They're actually heavily invested\nin touch and speech and gesture,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and also in senses --"},{"time":157800,"text":"things that can turn\ndumb objects, like cups,"},{"time":160560,"text":"and imbue them with the magic\nof the Internet,"},{"time":164400,"text":"potentially turning this digital cloud"},{"time":166800,"text":"into something we might touch and move."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169880,"text":"The parents in crisis over screen time"},{"time":172520,"text":"need physical digital toys\nteaching their kids to read,"},{"time":175680,"text":"as well as family-safe app stores."},{"time":179840,"text":"And I think, actually,\nthat's already really happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183720,"text":"Reality is richer than screens."},{"time":188640,"text":"For example, I love books."},{"time":192120,"text":"For me they are time machines --\natoms and molecules bound in space,"},{"time":197480,"text":"from the moment of their creation\nto the moment of my experience."},{"time":201480,"text":"But frankly,"},{"time":203040,"text":"the content's identical on my phone."},{"time":205440,"text":"So what makes this\na richer experience than a screen?"},{"time":209800,"text":"I mean, scientifically."},{"time":213440,"text":"We need screens, of course."},{"time":215320,"text":"I'm going to show film,\nI need the enormous screen."},{"time":220880,"text":"But there's more than you can do\nwith these magic boxes."},{"time":224880,"text":"Your phone is not\nthe Internet's door bitch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228920,"text":"We can build things --\nphysical things,"},{"time":231800,"text":"using physics and pixels,"},{"time":234320,"text":"that can integrate the Internet\ninto the world around us."},{"time":237011,"text":"And I'm going to show you\na few examples of those."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242480,"text":"A while ago, I got to work\nwith a design agency, Berg,"},{"time":245440,"text":"on an exploration of what the Internet\nwithout screens might actually look like."},{"time":250280,"text":"And they showed us a range ways"},{"time":252360,"text":"that light can work with simple senses\nand physical objects"},{"time":257320,"text":"to really bring the Internet to life,\nto make it tangible."},{"time":261640,"text":"Like this wonderfully mechanical\nYouTube player."},{"time":266560,"text":"And this was an inspiration to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270600,"text":"Next I worked with\nthe Japanese agency, AQ,"},{"time":273560,"text":"on a research project into mental health."},{"time":275920,"text":"We wanted to create an object"},{"time":277325,"text":"that could capture the subjective data\naround mood swings"},{"time":281080,"text":"that's so essential to diagnosis."},{"time":284040,"text":"This object captures your touch,"},{"time":286160,"text":"so you might press it\nvery hard if you're angry,"},{"time":289040,"text":"or stroke it if you're calm."},{"time":291200,"text":"It's like a digital emoji stick."},{"time":293840,"text":"And then you might revisit\nthose moments later,"},{"time":297040,"text":"and add context to them online."},{"time":299160,"text":"Most of all,"},{"time":300680,"text":"we wanted to create\nan intimate, beautiful thing"},{"time":304200,"text":"that could live in your pocket"},{"time":306160,"text":"and be loved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308753,"text":"The binoculars are actually\na birthday present"},{"time":310920,"text":"for the Sydney Opera House's\n40th anniversary."},{"time":313087,"text":"Our friends at Tellart in Boston\nbrought over a pair of street binoculars,"},{"time":317080,"text":"the kind you might find\non the Empire State Building,"},{"time":319581,"text":"and they fitted them with 360-degree views"},{"time":322440,"text":"of other iconic world heritage sights --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":325080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":326800,"text":"using Street View."},{"time":328840,"text":"And then we stuck them under the steps."},{"time":331920,"text":"So, they became this very physical,\nsimple reappropriation,"},{"time":336640,"text":"or like a portal to these other icons."},{"time":338720,"text":"So you might see Versailles\nor Shackleton's Hut."},{"time":341680,"text":"Basically, it's virtual\nreality circa 1955."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347440,"text":"In our office we use\nhacky sacks to exchange URLs."},{"time":350920,"text":"This is incredibly simple,\nit's like your Opal card."},{"time":353720,"text":"You basically put a website\non the little chip in here,"},{"time":357520,"text":"and then you do this and ... bosh! --"},{"time":361080,"text":"the website appears on your phone."},{"time":363440,"text":"It's about 10 cents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365960,"text":"Treehugger is a project\nthat we're working on"},{"time":368080,"text":"with Grumpy Sailor and Finch,\nhere in Sydney."},{"time":370520,"text":"And I'm very excited\nabout what might happen"},{"time":373440,"text":"when you pull the phones apart\nand you put the bits into trees,"},{"time":377280,"text":"and that my children\nmight have an opportunity"},{"time":380200,"text":"to visit an enchanted forest\nguided by a magic wand,"},{"time":384840,"text":"where they could talk to digital fairies\nand ask them questions,"},{"time":387880,"text":"and be asked questions in return."},{"time":390120,"text":"As you can see,"},{"time":391360,"text":"we're at the cardboard stage\nwith this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":394600,"text":"But I'm very excited"},{"time":395840,"text":"by the possibility of getting kids\nback outside without screens,"},{"time":399760,"text":"but with all the powerful magic\nof the Internet at their fingertips."},{"time":403720,"text":"And we hope to have something like this\nworking by the end of the year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409600,"text":"So let's recap."},{"time":411840,"text":"Humans like natural solutions."},{"time":413880,"text":"Humans love information."},{"time":415960,"text":"Humans need simple tools."},{"time":418640,"text":"These principles should underpin\nhow we design for the future,"},{"time":423640,"text":"not just for the Internet."},{"time":426040,"text":"You may feel uncomfortable about the age\nof information that we're moving into."},{"time":431720,"text":"You may feel challenged,\nrather than simply excited."},{"time":436200,"text":"Guess what? Me too."},{"time":438240,"text":"It's a really extraordinary period\nof human history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443840,"text":"We are the people\nthat actually build our world,"},{"time":447720,"text":"there are no artificial intelligences..."},{"time":449991,"text":"yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":453360,"text":"It's us -- designers, architects,\nartists, engineers."},{"time":458800,"text":"And if we challenge ourselves,"},{"time":461320,"text":"I think that actually\nwe can have a happy place"},{"time":465280,"text":"filled with the information we love"},{"time":467800,"text":"that feels as natural and as simple\nas switching on lightbulb."},{"time":472640,"text":"And although it may seem inevitable,"},{"time":474379,"text":"that what the public wants\nis watches and websites and widgets,"},{"time":479760,"text":"maybe we could give a bit of thought\nto cork and light and hacky sacks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485960,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487320,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}